title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Some Gave Some
description:
The Only Podcast That Matters™ has been exposed! After a bit of a break the band’s back together on Zoom as the Core 4 take on Cacti, loafers, quarantining again, the magic of the season’s first snow, Tenet, Tom Cruise, Pornhub, Shia LaBeouf and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
